      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Peel and slice <strong>half</strong> your <strong>red onion[s]</strong> thin rings (you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Add the<strong> onion rings</strong> to a shallow bowl with your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong> and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled red onion</strong></p>",
