    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the meat-free patty[ies] is cooked, remove the tray from the oven and top with the <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Return the tray to the oven for 3-4 min or until the cheese has melted – this is your <strong>cheesy meat-free patty</strong></p><p>While the cheese is melting, separate your<strong> lettuce </strong>into leaves, then wash them thoroughly and pat them dry with kitchen paper</p>",
