        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, top your <strong>toasted brioche base </strong>with a few <strong>lettuce</strong> <strong>leaves</strong>, a <strong>cheesy</strong> <strong>meat-free patty</strong>, some <strong>quick-pickled</strong> <strong>red</strong> <strong>onion</strong>, a dollop of <strong>chimichurri mayo</strong> and the <strong>toasted brioche lid </strong>– this is your<strong> cheesy veggie burger</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>chips</strong> to the side with any <strong>remaining chimichurri mayo </strong>and <strong>remaining lettuce leaves</strong></p><p>Top the lettuce leaves<strong> </strong>with any <strong>remaining quick-pickled onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
